---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Security - Moaiy" description="Security model and responsible disclosure process for Moaiy.">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-bg-primary py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Security</h1>
        <p class="font-body text-xl text-text-secondary">How Moaiy approaches encryption, key handling, and disclosure</p>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Core Principles</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-5">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Open Source</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm">Application code is public for review in GitHub repositories.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-5">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">OpenPGP Workflows</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm">Encryption and key-management flows are designed around OpenPGP-compatible tooling.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-5">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Local Key Handling</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm">Sensitive operations are performed locally in the app runtime environment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Current Security References</h2>
        <ul class="font-body text-text-secondary space-y-3">
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/SECURITY.md"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-accent-primary hover:underline"
            >
              moaiy/SECURITY.md
            </a>
            <span> - vulnerability reporting and response timeline.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/blob/main/DISCLAIMER.md"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-accent-primary hover:underline"
            >
              moaiy/DISCLAIMER.md
            </a>
            <span> - risk boundaries and responsibility notes.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/releases"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-accent-primary hover:underline"
            >
              Release Notes
            </a>
            <span> - versioned release assets and checksums.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">Report A Vulnerability</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Please do not disclose vulnerabilities in public issues. Use private disclosure channels so fixes can be
          prepared responsibly.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <a
            href="mailto:security@moaiy.com"
            class="bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-all"
          >
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Email</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm">security@moaiy.com</p>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/moaiy-com/moaiy/security/advisories"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-all"
          >
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">GitHub Advisories</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm">Use private advisory flow when enabled.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-bg-secondary to-bg-tertiary rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">User Security Checklist</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-primary rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Key Hygiene</h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm space-y-2">
              <li>• Keep private keys private.</li>
              <li>• Back up keys in secure storage.</li>
              <li>• Verify key fingerprints before trust/sign operations.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-bg-primary rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Release Hygiene</h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-text-secondary text-sm space-y-2">
              <li>• Download from official release channels only.</li>
              <li>• Verify checksums when available.</li>
              <li>• Keep app and OS versions up to date.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
